# Active Directory Helpdesk Assistant (Lite Version)

A lightweight, console-based PowerShell tool designed for IT Support Specialists and Helpdesk Technicians to quickly check user account status without opening ADUC.

## 🚀 Lite Version Features:
* Quick User Status Check (Enabled, Locked Out, Full Name, Password Last Set)
* 100% clean, documented, and production-ready code

---

## 🔥 GET THE FULL VERSION (Automation Kit)

Want to do more right from the console? The **Full Version** includes powerful automation features to streamline your daily workflow:

* **Instant Password Reset** (Automatically forces password change at next logon)
